Class WaitingQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.pds.Stage
      • main.java.pds.WaitingQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<OrderItem>

    public class WaitingQueue
extends Stage
implements java.lang.Iterable<OrderItem>, java.io.Serializable
    The WaitingQueue class is responsible for storing OrderItems before they are ready to go out for either delivery, cooking, or preparation.
